[http://p2pfoundation.net/Social_Venture#Social_Ven This page] was initiated by [[Ryan Lanham]] to support discussions occurring on the p2p Research mailing list, and on [http://www.facebook.com/home.php#/group.php?gid=72636396341&ref=mf Facebook] to support the development of micro social venture projects, financed by community contributions.

My interests to this topic also extend to collaborative governance and [http://p2pfoundation.net/Core_Peer-2-Peer_Collaboration_Principles P2P Collaboration Principles].